title: Forest
overview: A drama about a rescue 119 worker whose life goal is to have more than 5 trillion won in personal assets and a female doctor trying to get ahead in the nation's top university hospital, enter Miryung Forest where the wounded in soul gather.Kang San Hyuk is a member of the 119 special rescue team. He is handsome and smart, but he does not remember his childhood. Meanwhile, Jung Young Jae is an enthusiastic surgical resident.
